<component type="driver">
  <id>io.xilinx.xrt-xocl-dkms</id>
  <name>Xilinx XRT XOCL DKMS Drivers</name>
  <summary>Linux kernel drivers for Xilinx FPGA/ACAP devices</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      This package provides the Linux kernel drivers for Xilinx FPGA and Adaptive Compute Acceleration
      Platform (ACAP) devices. The drivers include management and user physical function drivers that
      enable PCIe-based datacenter platforms to work with the Xilinx Runtime (XRT).
    </p>
    <p>
      The package includes XOCL (Xilinx OpenCL) drivers for both management and user functions,
      providing device control, memory management, and compute acceleration capabilities.
    </p>
  </description>
